	New fields.
	(mourn_inferior): Define.
	(target_process_qsupported): Avoid the dangling else problem.
	(thread_stopped): Define.
	(pause_all): Define.
	(target_waitstatus_to_string): Declare.
	* target.c (target_waitstatus_to_string): New.

